title: Purina ONE High Protein, Natural Dry Kitten Food, +Plus Healthy Kitten Formula - 7 lb. Bag
description: Give your kitten the nutrition she needs with Purina ONE +Plus Healthy Kitten Formula dry cat food. Real chicken is the number 1 ingredient in this high protein dry kitten food, which supports growing muscles. Purina ONE for kittens uses a SmartBlend of high-quality ingredients, plus DHA, a nutrient found in mothers' milk, to help with brain and vision development. This natural kitten food has added vitamins, minerals and nutrients and accents of real vegetables with no artificial flavors or preservatives. The crunchy cat food kibble has an enticing texture, which, along with added calcium, helps support strong teeth and healthy gums. Four antioxidant sources, including vitamins E and A, help provide immune support for cats. She gets the 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition she needs to stay strong and healthy in this kitten dry food. Combining nature and research and formulated by a veterinarian-recommended brand, Purina ONE +Plus cat and kitten food offers results you can see in your cat.
